1
00:01:07,760 --> 00:01:09,820
Let's see who dares touch my husband.

2
00:01:10,960 --> 00:01:13,800
Song Xuan, we meet again.

3
00:01:13,880 --> 00:01:17,039
Seeing the man who killed your father and brother again,

4
00:01:17,039 --> 00:01:18,200
how does it feel?

5
00:01:18,240 --> 00:01:19,840
Are you in despair?

6
00:01:20,120 --> 00:01:21,160
King Bulei.

7
00:01:21,400 --> 00:01:24,800
Between the two of us, you're the one who despairs more often.

8
00:01:24,800 --> 00:01:25,720
Song Xuan.

9
00:01:26,600 --> 00:01:29,120
Even if I lose to you, so what?

10
00:01:29,560 --> 00:01:33,680
Your father and brother still died by my hand.

11
00:01:34,560 --> 00:01:36,000
If you keep provoking me,

12
00:01:36,120 --> 00:01:38,080
I don't mind crippling your right hand.

13
00:01:38,080 --> 00:01:40,520
Miss Song, we are here

14
00:01:40,560 --> 00:01:43,620
on the orders of the Grassland King to negotiate peace.

15
00:01:43,800 --> 00:01:45,130
Regarding past events,

16
00:01:45,280 --> 00:01:47,560
your emperor has decided not to pursue them.

17
00:01:47,560 --> 00:01:50,800
Please, Miss Song, consider the bigger picture.

18
00:01:50,960 --> 00:01:51,920
Princess Tuoya.

19
00:01:52,240 --> 00:01:53,800
You'd best keep your word.

20
00:01:55,520 --> 00:01:57,200
I heard you got married.

21
00:01:57,200 --> 00:01:59,080
To such an incompetent man.

22
00:01:59,080 --> 00:02:00,520
What a pity.

23
00:02:00,520 --> 00:02:01,600
Incompetent man?

24
00:02:02,680 --> 00:02:04,160
Are you talking about me?

25
00:02:04,480 --> 00:02:06,280
Why don't you go ask around?

26
00:02:06,760 --> 00:02:10,919
Everyone knows I'm the notorious Bai Manchuan.

27
00:02:14,360 --> 00:02:17,760
Your reputation is just a joke in the capital.

28
00:02:17,840 --> 00:02:21,000
You shouldn't judge a man by his appearance.

29
00:02:22,880 --> 00:02:24,240
Then what should I look at?

30
00:02:24,240 --> 00:02:25,960
Some people show off their sharpness,

31
00:02:25,960 --> 00:02:27,320
but are short-sighted.

32
00:02:27,600 --> 00:02:29,800
Some people seem unassuming,

33
00:02:29,960 --> 00:02:31,690
but plan every step carefully.

34
00:02:31,920 --> 00:02:33,400
As for my husband,

35
00:02:33,840 --> 00:02:35,280
time will tell.

36
00:02:35,480 --> 00:02:36,400
Song Xuan.

37
00:02:37,400 --> 00:02:39,040
No matter what you do,

38
00:02:39,079 --> 00:02:40,880
he will always be a piece of trash.

39
00:02:40,880 --> 00:02:42,360
If you're willing,

40
00:02:42,640 --> 00:02:44,360
you can come to me anytime.

41
00:02:44,360 --> 00:02:46,240
I think you have a death wish.

42
00:02:46,240 --> 00:02:47,680
Whether or not I'm trash,

43
00:02:47,680 --> 00:02:49,000
isn't for you to judge.

44
00:02:49,240 --> 00:02:51,880
You should learn from your father

45
00:02:52,240 --> 00:02:53,920
and be a coward.

46
00:03:07,720 --> 00:03:08,880
Trash.

47
00:03:50,200 --> 00:03:50,840
Stop!

48
00:03:58,360 --> 00:03:59,820
Greetings, Third Prince.

49
00:03:59,880 --> 00:04:02,240
The Prince and Princess have come from afar.

50
00:04:02,240 --> 00:04:04,240
Why didn't you enter the palace for an audience first,

51
00:04:04,240 --> 00:04:08,000
instead of coming to this house of pleasure to seek fun?

52
00:04:10,240 --> 00:04:11,480
We were idle,

53
00:04:11,480 --> 00:04:12,880
just looking for some fun.

54
00:04:12,880 --> 00:04:17,600
I didn't expect the subjects of Great Sheng to love having fun too.

55
00:04:17,600 --> 00:04:19,200
Since you are envoys from a foreign land,

56
00:04:19,200 --> 00:04:21,279
you must abide by Great Sheng's rules.

57
00:04:21,279 --> 00:04:23,840
How can we allow you to run wild here?

58
00:04:24,520 --> 00:04:26,050
Please excuse our manners.

59
00:04:26,120 --> 00:04:27,840
Since the breach of etiquette has occurred,

60
00:04:27,840 --> 00:04:30,000
Prince and Princess, please return to the relay station to rest.

61
00:04:30,000 --> 00:04:33,920
Tomorrow, I will personally take you two to the palace for an audience.

62
00:04:33,920 --> 00:04:34,920
Wait.

63
00:04:37,000 --> 00:04:38,960
I want to take this woman with me.

64
00:04:39,120 --> 00:04:41,040
She is the Second Miss of the Prime Minister's Manor.

65
00:04:41,040 --> 00:04:42,600
I'm afraid you can't take her.

66
00:04:42,600 --> 00:04:44,320
A noble lady?

67
00:04:44,800 --> 00:04:46,480
Now I want her even more.

68
00:04:46,680 --> 00:04:48,880
I'm afraid the Prince can't afford her.

69
00:04:49,800 --> 00:04:51,000
It's getting late.

70
00:04:51,360 --> 00:04:54,520
The Prince and Princess should go back and rest.

71
00:04:55,120 --> 00:04:55,920
Please.

72
00:04:58,560 --> 00:04:59,720
Miss Shen.

73
00:05:00,400 --> 00:05:02,520
We will definitely meet again.

74
00:05:10,120 --> 00:05:11,880
Manchuan, are you alright?

75
00:05:12,480 --> 00:05:13,200
I'm fine.

76
00:05:13,200 --> 00:05:15,840
Manchuan, can you walk me home?

77
00:05:16,080 --> 00:05:19,120
I should notify the Prime Minister's Mansion to pick up the Second Miss,

78
00:05:19,120 --> 00:05:21,200
to avoid any more trouble on the way.

79
00:05:21,400 --> 00:05:23,320
Why are you so nervous, Miss Song?

80
00:05:23,320 --> 00:05:25,050
Manchuan and I are old friends.

81
00:05:25,120 --> 00:05:26,850
I just asked him to walk me home.

82
00:05:27,560 --> 00:05:29,220
Are you afraid he'll run away?

83
00:05:29,800 --> 00:05:31,760
If my husband really wanted to leave,

84
00:05:31,760 --> 00:05:32,890
I wouldn't stop him.

85
00:05:35,200 --> 00:05:37,800
Then please continue to keep an eye on Manchuan, Miss Song.

86
00:05:37,800 --> 00:05:40,280
I hope if he really leaves in the future,

87
00:05:40,720 --> 00:05:41,800
you won't stop him.

88
00:05:42,240 --> 00:05:43,680
That day will never come.

89
00:05:46,800 --> 00:05:49,600
Madam Hua, find some people to escort Lingbo back.

90
00:05:50,760 --> 00:05:51,820
Someone come here!

91
00:05:59,480 --> 00:06:00,280
Let's go home.

92
00:06:13,240 --> 00:06:16,240
Bai Manchuan, how did you make your wife angry again?

93
00:06:17,680 --> 00:06:18,880
I didn't do anything.

94
00:06:18,960 --> 00:06:19,840
Do you know?

95
00:06:20,240 --> 00:06:21,560
What else could it be?

96
00:06:21,560 --> 00:06:23,020
Romantic entanglements.

97
00:06:23,040 --> 00:06:26,720
My brother went to the Baihua Brothel and got caught by my sister-in-law.

98
00:06:26,720 --> 00:06:28,800
How could you go to the Baihua Brothel?

99
00:06:28,800 --> 00:06:30,930
Have you lost your mind, you disgrace?

100
00:06:32,280 --> 00:06:34,720
I heard he went to find Shen Lingbo.

101
00:06:34,720 --> 00:06:36,400
And he even got into a fight.

102
00:06:37,800 --> 00:06:38,800
How... how...

103
00:06:38,800 --> 00:06:41,460
How did you get involved with Shen Lingbo again?

104
00:06:42,159 --> 00:06:43,090
What is going on?

105
00:06:44,360 --> 00:06:45,440
Bai Manchuan!

106
00:06:45,720 --> 00:06:47,920
I just went to watch the excitement.

107
00:06:48,520 --> 00:06:50,800
Haven't I told you ten thousand times

108
00:06:50,800 --> 00:06:53,640
not to get involved with people from the Prime Minister's Mansion?

109
00:06:53,640 --> 00:06:55,159
Why won't you listen?

110
00:06:56,200 --> 00:06:57,640
You unfilial son!

111
00:06:59,200 --> 00:07:00,480
To help your wife cool down,

112
00:07:00,480 --> 00:07:01,360
play along.

113
00:07:02,120 --> 00:07:03,320
Get ready, get ready.

114
00:07:03,680 --> 00:07:06,880
Let's see if you dare do it again.

115
00:07:07,320 --> 00:07:09,240
I've been talking to you for so long.

116
00:07:09,240 --> 00:07:10,240
Let's see if you...

117
00:07:10,240 --> 00:07:11,480
I really know I was wrong.

118
00:07:11,480 --> 00:07:12,680
I'll beat you to death!

119
00:07:12,680 --> 00:07:13,480
I'll kill you!

120
00:07:13,560 --> 00:07:14,840
Spare me, please.

121
00:07:14,840 --> 00:07:16,480
Let's see if you learn your lesson.

122
00:07:16,480 --> 00:07:18,240
Dad, I know I was wrong.

123
00:07:18,560 --> 00:07:20,480
I won't dare do it again, Dad.

124
00:07:21,840 --> 00:07:23,000
It hurts so much.

125
00:07:23,400 --> 00:07:24,240
Let's eat.

126
00:07:25,840 --> 00:07:26,840
Bastard!

127
00:07:26,960 --> 00:07:28,240
Bastard! Bastard!

128
00:07:28,360 --> 00:07:31,520
Bastard! Bastard! Bastard!

129
00:07:31,520 --> 00:07:32,280
Bastard!

130
00:07:32,560 --> 00:07:33,640
Get away!

131
00:07:33,640 --> 00:07:35,200
Stop bullying Chuyi!

132
00:07:35,320 --> 00:07:36,000
Get him!

133
00:07:36,840 --> 00:07:37,200
Bastard!

134
00:07:37,200 --> 00:07:38,400
Hit him! Hit him!

135
00:07:38,760 --> 00:07:39,120
Bastard!

136
00:07:39,120 --> 00:07:39,800
What are you doing?

137
00:07:39,800 --> 00:07:40,600
Shoo! Shoo!

138
00:07:41,159 --> 00:07:42,200
If anyone bullies Chuyi again,

139
00:07:42,200 --> 00:07:43,400
I'll break your legs!

140
00:07:46,760 --> 00:07:49,040
Adai, are you okay?

141
00:07:49,400 --> 00:07:50,200
I'm fine.

142
00:07:50,520 --> 00:07:52,800
Child, why didn't you fight back?

143
00:07:52,800 --> 00:07:55,400
I can't cause trouble for the Marquis Mansion.

144
00:07:55,720 --> 00:07:57,250
I've told you so many times,

145
00:07:57,400 --> 00:07:58,400
you are my sister.

146
00:07:58,400 --> 00:08:00,120
There's no such thing as trouble.

147
00:08:00,120 --> 00:08:02,450
Why didn't I see this child at the wedding?

148
00:08:03,080 --> 00:08:04,160
Her name is Chuyi.

149
00:08:04,520 --> 00:08:06,360
She's been at the academy these past few days.

150
00:08:06,360 --> 00:08:08,160
She is a child my father adopted.

151
00:08:08,800 --> 00:08:10,040
I see.

152
00:08:18,480 --> 00:08:19,920
Shen Lingbo.

153
00:08:20,680 --> 00:08:22,240
You're in quite the mood.

154
00:08:22,640 --> 00:08:24,640
You just got back from Baihua Tower,

155
00:08:24,800 --> 00:08:27,200
and you're already drowning your sorrows.

156
00:08:27,240 --> 00:08:28,500
None of your business.

157
00:08:28,760 --> 00:08:29,800
You were just at Baihua Tower.

158
00:08:29,800 --> 00:08:32,200
It's bad enough you embarrassed yourself,

159
00:08:32,200 --> 00:08:35,039
but you had to provoke the Grand Prince of the Grasslands.

160
00:08:35,039 --> 00:08:36,000
Do you have any idea?

161
00:08:36,000 --> 00:08:38,600
He publicly demanded you from Father at court.

162
00:08:38,600 --> 00:08:40,530
He wants to take you as a concubine.

163
00:08:40,760 --> 00:08:42,960
You've completely humiliated Father.

164
00:08:44,120 --> 00:08:46,120
What is Father's dignity worth?

165
00:08:46,960 --> 00:08:48,600
Stop being so stubborn.

166
00:08:48,800 --> 00:08:51,840
Father was so furious he smashed several treasures in his study.

167
00:08:51,840 --> 00:08:54,920
You are a disgrace to the Shen family.

168
00:08:55,160 --> 00:08:56,680
You'd better shut up now.

169
00:08:56,680 --> 00:08:59,240
What? Did I hit a nerve?

170
00:09:04,120 --> 00:09:05,360
Are you crazy?

171
00:09:08,200 --> 00:09:09,730
Didn't I tell you to shut up?

172
00:09:09,800 --> 00:09:11,320
Why do you insist on provoking me?

173
00:09:11,320 --> 00:09:12,400
Let go of me!

174
00:09:13,600 --> 00:09:14,800
You lunatic!

175
00:09:15,120 --> 00:09:16,360
You'll regret this.

176
00:09:16,360 --> 00:09:17,880
Self-righteous people like you

177
00:09:17,880 --> 00:09:19,800
are in no position to make me regret anything.

178
00:09:19,800 --> 00:09:21,360
I really will kill you.

179
00:09:21,680 --> 00:09:23,720
Father, save me!

180
00:09:25,560 --> 00:09:27,360
Remember, don't cross me.

181
00:09:30,320 --> 00:09:32,520
Shen Lingbo is bullying me!

182
00:09:33,600 --> 00:09:34,360
Go back.

183
00:09:35,040 --> 00:09:35,840
Go back.

184
00:09:41,080 --> 00:09:43,410
Do you really think no one can control you?

185
00:09:44,200 --> 00:09:46,800
You're acting recklessly. Have you lost your mind?

186
00:09:46,800 --> 00:09:48,560
Why so angry, Father?

187
00:09:48,560 --> 00:09:51,280
Do you think Bulei is a good man?

188
00:09:51,840 --> 00:09:54,120
Who told you he was my target tonight?

189
00:09:54,120 --> 00:09:55,760
What exactly are you up to?

190
00:09:57,960 --> 00:09:59,880
I always know my limits.

191
00:09:59,960 --> 00:10:04,640
Unlike you, Father. You frame people but leave so much evidence behind.

192
00:10:05,280 --> 00:10:06,400
What do you mean?

193
00:10:09,480 --> 00:10:12,680
Why did the assassins from Marquis Zhongyi's Manor come for you?

194
00:10:12,680 --> 00:10:15,600
Don't you know?

195
00:10:19,840 --> 00:10:21,560
I warned you long ago.

196
00:10:21,840 --> 00:10:23,480
Don't try to set me up.

197
00:10:23,480 --> 00:10:24,840
Shen Lingbo.

198
00:10:25,320 --> 00:10:26,040
You...

199
00:10:26,040 --> 00:10:26,800
Shh.

200
00:10:28,800 --> 00:10:31,480
I just hope that next time,

201
00:10:31,720 --> 00:10:33,520
you consider the consequences.

202
00:10:33,800 --> 00:10:36,640
Make the wrong move,

203
00:10:36,640 --> 00:10:38,560
and there's no turning back.
